data.description: If you're looking for a country setting that offers some privacy with a home sitting on a corner lot of 1.73 acres, 4819 Deerwood Road may just be the perfect one for you! Featuring two bedrooms, two full bathrooms, a metal roof, new HVAC, a large outside sunroom with a mini-split for cooling and heating, and the most relaxing screened-in front porch, this property has so much to offer. When walking in from the front porch, you enter the living room. To the right of the living room is a quaint kitchen full of character and a new stainless steel refrigerator. From there, you can enter the dining area and then through a door to one of the bedrooms. Also from the living room, you can enter the other bedroom that houses a large walk-in closet or another room that is a flexible space to use however you wish. A large two-car carport, an outbuilding for your special home projects or to use as a workshop, an outdoor fire pit, a large fenced-in area within the yard, fresh landscaping, and a variety of trees highlight this space to be one where you will want to spend all of your upcoming days and evenings. This home also comes with a transferable termite bond. Call today to see about turning this house into your home!
